snippet.title: [OLD] Super Mario and the Rainbow Stars - Demo Release Trailer [SMBX 1.4.5]
snippet.description:
After more than 4 years of hard work, it is finally here, the demo of SMATRS! 
Adventure through the entirety of the first chapter of the game, featuring many new gimmicks, cutscenes, bosses and more! Have fun :)

Please note: This demo is outdated and a new demo is coming out for SMBX2.
Download: https://www.smbxgame.com/forums/viewtopic.php?p=371064

Need help? Join the SMATRS Discord:
https://discord.gg/GBXUa7NF2J 

#smbx #smatrs
